title: [Empath Guild, Entrance]
description: Wisteria and rose vines drape over a latticework arch of bamboo.  Their fragrance is nearly overwhelming, yet there is an underlying chemical tang in the air.  Large, rounded stones form a path to and from the arch, creating a V shape.  Moss surrounds the stones, and ferns line the path.
tags: meta:mapname:Isle of the Four Winds - Empath Guild
